        <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;background:#0C7BA8;"></div>
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 10px;">WD17–WD25</p>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 10px;letter-spacing:-0.02em;">Watford</h3>
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#64748B;line-height:1.65;margin:0 0 16px;">A mix of Victorian terraces, 1930s semis, and newer builds. Common issues include failing pebble dash on postwar stock and settlement cracks in older properties.</p>
